余波之上，深刻描绘一个家族在战火中如何成长、并共同守护血脉相连的情感纽带的历程，从而将故事推向更具张力的全新维度。此外，潘多拉的全新领域也即将揭晓——观众将首次邂逅“风之商人”这个崇尚和平的全新游牧民族，他们乘坐独特的浮空生物飞船穿梭于各部落间，交易货物、传递信息。\r\n　　而更具颠覆性的是“灰烬族”的登场，这个以掠夺为生、性情凶猛的族群，与大地之母爱娃之间有着深刻的矛盾。他们的出现，将撕开潘多拉不为人知的黑暗传说。当弑亲之仇与部落恩怨交织，潘多拉的命运悬于一线——在这场跨文明的复仇之战中，人类与纳威族将如何抉择，才能真正守护各自的家园与未来？<\/p>","vod_play_from":"snm3u8","vod_play_server":"no","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"HD$https:\/\/v14.yuglf.com\/202603\/29\/wNnzmHNTL927\/video\/index.m3u8","vod_down_from":"","vod_down_server":"","vod_down_note":"","vod_down_url":"","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type_name":"动作片"},{"vod_id":142692,"type_id":6,"type_id_1":1,"group_id":0,"vod_name":"歼灭者觉醒","vod_sub":"","vod_en":"jianmiezhejuexing","vod_status":1,"vod_letter":"J","vod_color":"","vod_tag":"","vod_class":"动作,剧情","vod_pic":"https:\/\/snzypic.vip\/upload\/vod\/20260328-1\/ba58375ad9d296de8b124e268db3c6c8.jpg","vod_pic_thumb":"","vod_pic_slide":"","vod_pic_screenshot":"","vod_actor":"Dan,Arora,Bobby,Sharma,Pratik,Sehajpal,Tanya,Davis,Kevin,Tan,Kevin,Tan,Beck,Rosser","vod_director":"Waqar,Peter,Gill","vod_writer":"","vod_behind":"","vod_blurb":"　　一位离群索居的前贩毒集团成员在救下一名歌手免遭杀害后，又卷入了新的血腥冲突之中。与此同时，一位心怀复仇之心的犯罪头目也对他发起了攻击，想要对他进行报复。","vod_remarks":"HD中字","vod_pubdate":"","vod_total":0,"vod_serial":"0","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"美国","vod_lang":"英语","vod_year":"2026","vod_version":"","vod_state":"","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":0,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":0,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":716,"vod_hits_day":822,"vod_hits_week":768,"vod_hits_month":730,"vod_duration":"119","vod_up":828,"vod_down":661,"vod_score":"1.0","vod_score_all":610,"vod_score_num":610,"vod_time":"2026-03-28 20:05:51","vod_time_add":1774699479,"vod_time_hits":0,"vod_time_make":0,"vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":0,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_p